<div class="contentpaneldark">
    <h1>Application Hosting Plans</h1>
    <p>
      When you need your <em>application</em> online and not just the server it sits on.
    </p>
    <p>
      All of our plans include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>100% uptime guarantee for approved applications (less scheduled downtime)</li>
      <li>Application monitoring and automated notifications</li>
      <li>Response time guarantee</li>
    </ul>

    <div id="hostingplans" class="ui-tabs-hide">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#shared1">Shared 1</a></li>
        <li><a href="#shared2">Shared 2</a></li>
        <li><a href="#shared3">Shared 3</a></li>
        <li><a href="#ded1">Dedicated 1</a></li>
        <li><a href="#ded2">Dedicated 2</a></li>
        <li><a href="#custom">Custom</a></li>
      </ul>

      <div id="shared1" class="plan">
        <h2>Shared Application Hosting 1</h2>
        <p>Designed for applications where cost is a concern, and that service less than 10,000 user sessions per month.</p>
        <h3>Technical Details</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Application Server
            <ul>
              <li>2 Mongrel instances (Rails)</li>
              <li>Tomcat instance (Java)</li>
            </ul></li>
          <li>Apache balancer / accelerator</li>
          <li>MySQL or PostgreSQL database</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div id="shared2" class="plan">
        <h2>Shared Application Hosting 2</h2>
        <p>Designed for applications that require more CPU horsepower to do their job, and that service less than 100,000 user sessions per month.</p>
        <h3>Technical Details</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Application Server
            <ul>
              <li>4 Mongrel instances across two servers (Rails)</li>
              <li>JBoss or Glassfish instance (Java)</li>
            </ul></li>
          <li>Apache balancer</li>
          <li>Squid accelerator (optional)</li>
          <li>MySQL or PostgreSQL database</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div id="shared3" class="plan">
        <h2>Shared Application Hosting 3</h2>
        <p>Designed for business critical applications that require some CPU horsepower and high availability and service less than 300,000 user sessions per month.</p>
        <h3>Technical Details</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Application Server
            <ul>
              <li>12 Mongrel instances across two servers (Rails)</li>
              <li>Two JBoss or Glassfish instances across two servers (Java)</li>
            </ul></li>
          <li>Apache balancer</li>
          <li>Squid accelerator (optional)</li>
          <li>MySQL or PostgreSQL database</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div id="ded1" class="plan">
        <h2>Dedicated Application Hosting 1</h2>
        <p>Designed for business sensitive applications that cannot be co-located with other applications on the same hardware due to strict privacy concerns, that require a specific server configuration, or require isolation for a private network connection to a corporate network.</p>
        <h3>Technical Details</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Application Server
            <ul>
              <li>Dedicated server hardware
              <ul>
                <li>System optimized Mongrel instances (Rails)</li>
                <li>JBoss or Glassfish instance (Java)</li>
              </ul></li>
            </ul></li>
          <li>Apache balancer (separate device)</li>
          <li>Squid accelerator (optional, separate device)</li>
          <li>Choice of Windows or Linux operating system</li>
          <li>Oracle, MySQL or PostgreSQL database on Linux or Windows</li>
          <li>MS SQL Express or Standard database on Windows (MS SQL Standard licensing priced separately)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div id="ded2" class="plan">
        <h2>Dedicated Application Hosting 2</h2>
        <p>Designed for business critical and business sensitive applications that cannot be co-located with other applications and where the up-time of the application is critical. Two dedicated servers provide hot-failover and high performance.</p>
        <h3>Technical Details</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Application Server
            <ul>
              <li>Two dedicated servers
              <ul>
                <li>System optimized Mongrel instances (Rails)</li>
                <li>JBoss or Glassfish instances on each (Java)</li>
              </ul></li>
            </ul></li>
          <li>Apache balancer (separate device)</li>
          <li>Squid accelerator (optional, separate device)</li>
          <li>Choice of Windows or Linux operating system</li>
          <li>Oracle, MySQL or PostgreSQL database on Linux or Windows</li>
          <li>MS SQL Express or Standard database on Windows (MS SQL Standard licensing priced separately)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div id="custom" class="plan">
        <h2>Custom Application Hosting</h2>
        <p>For complex customer requirements, a custom crafted environment can be designed by our experts to meet just about any demands. Multiple physical data-centers with geo-sensitive load balancing, segmented network traffic, custom router, firewall and inter-network linkage requirements. We will work with you to find the optimal configuration for your budget and requirements.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
